data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home close to I-35 in desirable Comal ISD. This home has been updated with a new roof with transferrable warranty and a new water heater!. The home features cute front porch, a large backyard with covered patio, deck, and play yard is included ready to entertain! Inside the home you will find a large kitchen with ample counter space, plenty of cabinets, a kitchen island, corner pantry, eat in breakfast area and bar, and refrigerator is also included. Large primary bedroom, bath, half bath, and laundry all located on the main floor with washer and dryer included. Upstairs has a great flex space that could be used for a home office/craft/study area, in addition to the game/media room, 3 bedrooms and a bathroom. Close to shopping and restaurants, quick access to downtown New Braunfels, San Antonio/Austin, and all the fun this area has to offer! Schedule your appointment now!
